    <item>
      <title>欧盟表示已准备好结束与波兰的法治争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/eu-says-it-s-ready-to-end-rule-of-law-dispute-with-poland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟即将结束与波兰因前民族主义政府领导下的民主倒退而长期存在的争端，这为总理唐纳德·图斯克提供了动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/eu-says-it-s-ready-to-end-rule-of-law-dispute-with-poland</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 12:43:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
