    <item>
      <title>乍得选举开始，军政府领导人寻求合法化夺权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/chad-vote-begins-as-junta-leader-looks-to-legitimize-power-grab</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍得民众周一开始投票，人们普遍预计军事领导人穆罕默德·代比将获胜，这一结果将有助于他三年前父亲去世后夺取权力的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/chad-vote-begins-as-junta-leader-looks-to-legitimize-power-grab</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:15:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京上任前夕下令进行战术核演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其第五个总统任期就职前一天，俄罗斯总统普京下令俄罗斯军队进行涉及战术核武器的作战演习，此举加剧了他与西方的对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 07:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
